</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Warcraft 被指黑人角色太多   NPC 變有色人種惹爭議</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/26/world-of-warcraft-turmoil-around-sudden-appearance-of-people-of-colour-is-surprisingly-complex/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=world-of-warcraft-turmoil-around-sudden-appearance-of-people-of-colour-is-surprisingly-complex</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 26 Dec 2021 02:04:05 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[blizzard]]></category><category><![CDATA[有色人種]]></category><category><![CDATA[魔獸]]></category><category><![CDATA[魔獸世界]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077547</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>遊戲《魔獸世界》近年作出多項改進，由 2020 年起，白人角色的膚色發生變化，今年 9 月更加入了更多有色人種 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>遊戲《魔獸世界》近年作出多項改進，由 2020 年起，白人角色的膚色發生變化，今年 9 月更加入了更多有色人種。近日《魔獸世界》一個非官方 Discord 群組為此進行熱烈討論，許多玩家抱怨 Blizzard 將《魔獸世界》NPC 變為有色人種，更有人調侃「暴風城中黑人太多了」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077548" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/E3E1E53E-0615-4B54-AF43-90529FC44F42-694x165.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="165" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/E3E1E53E-0615-4B54-AF43-90529FC44F42-694x165.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/E3E1E53E-0615-4B54-AF43-90529FC44F42-1280x304.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/E3E1E53E-0615-4B54-AF43-90529FC44F42-768x183.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/E3E1E53E-0615-4B54-AF43-90529FC44F42.jpeg 1329w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0FDF7B5F-B2FD-4444-8980-F2FB7CA65879-694x371.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0FDF7B5F-B2FD-4444-8980-F2FB7CA65879-694x371.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0FDF7B5F-B2FD-4444-8980-F2FB7CA65879-1280x685.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0FDF7B5F-B2FD-4444-8980-F2FB7CA65879-768x411.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0FDF7B5F-B2FD-4444-8980-F2FB7CA65879.jpeg 1318w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1F0B5184-1656-4132-9B1D-E105F4DFFF92-694x556.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1F0B5184-1656-4132-9B1D-E105F4DFFF92-694x556.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1F0B5184-1656-4132-9B1D-E105F4DFFF92-768x615.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1F0B5184-1656-4132-9B1D-E105F4DFFF92.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9376BF6E-C105-42D6-B1DA-8EAD01BF05EC-694x198.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="198" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9376BF6E-C105-42D6-B1DA-8EAD01BF05EC-694x198.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9376BF6E-C105-42D6-B1DA-8EAD01BF05EC-768x219.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9376BF6E-C105-42D6-B1DA-8EAD01BF05EC.jpeg 1176w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">名為 Seat of the Council 的 Discord 群組經常會討論有關《魔獸世界》的遊戲改進，近日就圍繞「暴風城中黑人太多」引發爭議，對於《魔獸世界》是否應該加入黑人、原住民及其他有色人種，群組成員的意見各不相同。有意見認為 Blizzard 為求政治正確，刻意作出「洗白」的改動，認為現時遊戲中有太多黑人角色。現時頻道已經被封，對話記錄亦已被清空，但據聞成員已在另一個服務器創建群組，爭論仍在持續。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30-363x580.jpeg" alt="" width="363" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30-363x580.jpeg 363w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30-564x900.jpeg 564w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30-768x1226.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30-962x1536.jpeg 962w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CA5818CA-3E3F-4603-9453-1D902A8D5C30.jpeg 1002w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 363px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有指是次爭論大多由一名 ID 為 Asjon 的用户引發，他認為 Blizzard 只是故意把某些白人 NPC 的膚色塗黑，當中的多樣及包容性只是一種懶惰的迎合行為；Blizzard 也未有解釋這些「特殊」 NPC 的由來，例如跨性別群體存在等。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/MShieldbreaker/status/1471557514978373633">Twitter</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
